Read this --- and then NEVER wear a mask again unless you absolutely have to. I wear tissue paper when I have to enter a business that requires one - not a biggie if what I need is important - BUT - unlike the absolute idiots I see all around me: The phony mask doesn't go on until I go in 'their' door and it comes off the instant I open the door to leave. I can't believe the absolute uninformed idiots that are walking down the street WEARING A FRIGGIN' MASK or driving their car - BY THEMSELVES and wearing a chin diaper pulled up over their nose. Masks are only a control mechanism BUT you can fight [their] attempts at absolute control by NOT damaging your health by destroying your oxygen supply. READ IT and then take your mask off and take that disgusting, ugly, slave-control mechanism OFF YOUR FRIGGIN' CHILDREN! And if you can't go anyplace - DON'T GO! The lives of you and your children are a FCK lot more important than being able to spend money in Walmart!

Can we unmask these assholes posing as Patriots?!? Surely the FBI could figure this out in a hot minute.... they proved that they can actually solve crimes with the Nashville bomber
Fuck masks
I can see clearly now your mask is on and it's going to be a bright, bright sun shiny day!  Friends, family and foes!
